        Attributes used to style the Action Bar.

        Includes the following attributes:

        AttributeDescription
        com.example.spoon.ordering:background Specifies a background drawable for the action bar.
        com.example.spoon.ordering:backgroundSplit Specifies a background drawable for the bottom component of a split action bar.
        com.example.spoon.ordering:backgroundStacked Specifies a background drawable for a second stacked row of the action bar.
        com.example.spoon.ordering:customNavigationLayout Specifies a layout for custom navigation.
        com.example.spoon.ordering:displayOptions Options affecting how the action bar is displayed.
        com.example.spoon.ordering:divider Specifies the drawable used for item dividers.
        com.example.spoon.ordering:height Specifies a fixed height.
        com.example.spoon.ordering:homeLayout Specifies a layout to use for the "home" section of the action bar.
        com.example.spoon.ordering:icon Specifies the drawable used for the application icon.
        com.example.spoon.ordering:indeterminateProgressStyle Specifies a style resource to use for an indeterminate progress spinner.
        com.example.spoon.ordering:itemPadding Specifies padding that should be applied to the left and right sides of system-provided items in the bar.
        com.example.spoon.ordering:logo Specifies the drawable used for the application logo.
        com.example.spoon.ordering:navigationMode The type of navigation to use.
        com.example.spoon.ordering:progressBarPadding Specifies the horizontal padding on either end for an embedded progress bar.
        com.example.spoon.ordering:progressBarStyle Specifies a style resource to use for an embedded progress bar.
        com.example.spoon.ordering:subtitle Specifies subtitle text used for navigationMode="normal"
        com.example.spoon.ordering:subtitleTextStyle Specifies a style to use for subtitle text.
